052    * Hint that the media resource can be started automatically when the page is loaded.
053    *
054    * @param autoplay
055    *    The new value for this attribute.
056    *    Typically a {@link Boolean} or {@link String}.
057    * @return This object.
058    */

061      return this;
062   }
